data.name: Classic Garden Salad with Grilled Chicken
data.quickTastyDescription: A fresh and vibrant garden salad topped with perfectly grilled chicken for a satisfying meal.
detailedCookingInstructions: Wash and prepare the salad greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and carrot.
Slice the cucumber and carrot into thin strips.
Cut the avocado in half, remove the pit, and slice it.
Grill the chicken breast until fully cooked, then slice it into strips.
In a large bowl, combine the salad greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, carrot, and avocado.
Top the salad with the grilled chicken strips.
Drizzle olive oil and balsamic vinegar over the salad.
Season with salt, black pepper, dried oregano, and garlic powder to taste.
